# Frontend Calendar Development Standards

## FullCalendar.js Integration
- Use version-specific CDN links for consistency
- Initialize calendar with proper Lithuanian locale settings
- Implement custom event rendering for ExoClass activities
- Use proper event click handlers for navigation

## Event Display Standards
- Show activity type with proper icons and gradients
- Display availability status (Available, Limited, Full)
- Include teacher/instructor information
- Format times according to Lithuanian standards (24-hour format)

## Responsive Design Requirements
- Mobile-first CSS approach
- Touch-friendly interface elements
- Flexible grid layouts that adapt to screen sizes
- Proper font scaling for readability

## CSS Organization
